{"tid":1519860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府既春袋已經好明顯啦！特區政府急了！","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:17:55.000Z","uid":29917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"323ece1af2853579572ca598c0a2af41f21474ee","tid":1519860,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"政府既春袋已經好明顯啦！特區政府急了！<br />\n<br />\n從多名人仕及議員被捕，被襲，連登吹風所謂既 end game，仲有藍絲谷瘋傳有警員被襲<br />\n多樣事件俾人睇到一樣野，政府開始急，想係831解決成個運動！<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講？<br />\n前線唔會咁得閒同你講咩end game, 因為佢地一直處於下風，處於被動既狀態<br />\n點解要不發不反對通知書？831遊行如果如常，唔會有突破，中聯辦一定駐重兵，示威者可以點？<br />\n藍絲谷又瘋傳警員被斬，呢d橋段過去幾次大遊行前一晚見慣見熟<br />\n<br />\n種種事件只會令我地聯想到九一機場係政府既春袋，大家如果係愛國愛港既，唔應該搞亂香港，因為機場對香港真係好重要。"},{"pid":"9b084af361edfad094c41548f1677aa52639f403","tid":1519860,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入來推po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"260f50e5e902ba5739f95c38e3a7f4b6803b7cf3","tid":1519860,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"